  "description": {
   "en": "Edogawa Ranpo's masterpiece \"Black Lizard\" is adapted comically and adorable by Hiromi Morishita of \"Shonen Ashibe\" and \"Osaka Hamlet\"! The breathtaking battle between the great detective Kogoro Akechi and the female phantom thief Black Lizard unfolds in a funny way. \"Black Lizard\" is one of Edogawa's most popular works. It has been used in various productions such as movies, dramas and plays. It is widely accepted by Ranpo Edogawa fans, mystery novel fans, Kogoro Akechi fans, Akihiro Miwa fans, and traditional Hiromi Morishita fans."
